3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The use of genetic programming to evolve optimisers can be considered a form of machine learning. 
4. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper deals with the design and analysis of local optimisation algorithms, which is a core topic in data structures and algorithms.
